getElectronCount

public int getElectronCount()
                     throws CMLException
generates the number of electrons. requires molecule to have been set uses the basis set to count the electrons. Thus a minimal basis set for the first 2 rows will count just the valence electrond (H=1, Li=1, ... F=7) and adjust for overall charge.

Returns:
electron count or 0 if molecule or basis not set
Throws:
CMLException - unsupported basis
